name: Tom Cruise embedding
description:
Tom Cruise textual embedd,
To use this file,

  • Download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder

  • Then simply add ToCru69 as part of your prompt and the handsometom Cruise will be the star of your image!!

  • Keep the Samples <30 and CFG scale at 7, although these values depend on the length of your prompt I found about values work best for me.

    Imp. Note !!!! : Some images may turn up b&w due to 2-3 images in training being b&w, if you get a b&w image just generate another one, thank you.

    Do check out my other embedds https://civitai.com/user/dogu_cate
